    %p
      This is an
      %a{:href => 'http://opencityapps.org'} Open City
      project done as a volunteer effort. We built this site because we think more Chicagoans (including ourselves) should be involved in their local communities.

    %p
      The team is:

    %ul
      %li
        %a{:href => "http://derekeder.com"} Derek Eder
        \- developer and designer
      %li
