        \- developer

    %hr
    %h4#data Data

    %p
      This site was built with calendar and event from the Chicago Police Department
      = succeed '.' do
        %a{:href => 'http://api1.chicagopolice.org/clearpath/'} ClearPath API

    %p 
      The District and Beat boundary data is stored in Google Fusion Tables and are open for anyone to use:

    %ul
      %li
        %a{:href => 'https://www.google.com/fusiontables/DataSource?docid=1fYRn1iHFY65w6QAEzBoPnw-SHtwvgWO2zeyCrkU'} Police District Boundaries
